#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Data URLs allow small document data to be included in the &URL; itself. This "
"is useful for very small &HTML; testcases or other occasions that do not "
"justify a document of their own."
msgstr ""
"Podatkovni URL-ji dovoljujejo vključevanje manjših podatkov o dokumentih v "
"samem &URL;. To je uporabno za zelo majhne &HTML; testne primere ali ob "
"drugih priložnostih, ko samostojen dokument ni potreben."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>data:,foobar</userinput> (note the comma after the colon) will "
"deliver a text document that contains nothing but <literal>foobar</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>data:,vnos</userinput> (pazite na vejico za dvopičjem) dostavi "
"besedilni dokument, ki vsebuje le <literal>vnos</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The last example delivered a text document. For &HTML; documents one has to "
"specify the &MIME; type <literal>text/html</literal>: <quote><userinput>data:"
"text/html,&lt;title&gt;Testcase&lt;/title&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is a testcase&lt;/"
"p&gt;</userinput></quote>. This will produce exactly the same output as if "
"the content had been loaded from a document of its own."
msgstr ""
"V prejšnjem primeru je bil dostavljen besedilni dokument, če pa želite "
"&HTML; dokument, je potrebno navesti tip &MIME; <literal>text/html</"
"literal>: <quote><userinput>data:text/html,&lt;title&gt;Testni Primer&lt;/"
"title&gt;&lt;p&gt;To je testni primer&lt;/p&gt;</userinput></quote>. To bo "
"ustvarilo popolnoma enak rezultat, kot če bi bila vsebina naložena iz "
"lastnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specifying alternate character sets is also possible. Note that 8-Bit "
"characters have to be escaped by a percentage sign and their two-digit "
"hexadecimal codes: <quote><userinput>data:;charset=iso-8859-1,Gr%FC%DFe aus "
"Schl%E4gl</userinput></quote> results in <quote><literal>Gr&uuml;&szlig;e "
"aus Schl&auml;gl</literal></quote> whereas omitting the charset attribute "
"might lead to something like <quote><literal>Gr??e aus Schl?gl</literal></"
"quote>."
msgstr ""
"Specifikacija alternativnega nabora znakov je tudi mogoča. Opozarjamo, da "
"morajo biti 8-bitni znaki posebno obravnavani z znakom za odstotek in "
"napisani z njihovo dvomestno šestnajstiško kodo: <quote><userinput>data:;"
"charset=iso-8859-1,Gr%FC%DFe aus Schl%E4gl</userinput></quote> se prikaže "
"kot <quote><literal>Gr&uuml;&szlig;e aus Schl&auml;gl</literal></quote>, če "
"pa izpustimo atribut charset pa dobimo nekaj takega: <quote><literal>Gr??e "
"aus Schl?gl</literal></quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2397.txt\">IETF RFC2397</ulink> "
"provides more information."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2397.txt\">IETF RFC2397</ulink> "
"ponuja več informacij."
